<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-1954] Regression: Some lines are too small / too long</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-1954</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The attached images have differences in line thickness / length. The vattenfall file had this problem before, it was solved in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-1830&quot; title=&quot;Grey background rectangle rendered at different position&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-1830&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-1830&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
